    "description": "在这款宁静的游戏中放松身心，照顾你最喜欢的小居民：水豚！制作满足它们需求的菜单，让它们开心，并发展您的公园<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >享受舒适的游戏</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104120/extras/ea1c816cdb66ff33353baa4e13252950.webp?t=1747833264\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>学学水豚，让自己舒服点，玩得开心点。没有时间压力<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104120/extras/717b6fab60e55e951160082839de2c2d.poster.avif?t=1747833264\" width=426 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104120/extras/717b6fab60e55e951160082839de2c2d.webm?t=1747833264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104120/extras/717b6fab60e55e951160082839de2c2d.mp4?t=1747833264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造和装饰自己的公园</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104120/extras/ea1c816cdb66ff33353baa4e13252950.webp?t=1747833264\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>精心设计和装饰您的水豚围栏。解锁新的装饰和舒适功能，提高您的水豚的生活质量。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104120/extras/d0e0b0b349ead2fa2aabaeae35482962.poster.avif?t=1747833264\" width=426 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104120/extras/d0e0b0b349ead2fa2aabaeae35482962.webm?t=1747833264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104120/extras/d0e0b0b349ead2fa2aabaeae35482962.mp4?t=1747833264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适应每只水豚的特殊需求</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://s